Overall Rating 3.8⭐️ If you’re in the area definitely give it a try! Pros: Monte’s has great pizza and good, respectable service! When I first moved to the area I would order large pies almost 3-4x per week for my family. The pasta dishes , like Baked Ziti make my day! The neighborhood environment is lively, bustling and bright. The services was warm, attentive and professional. Cons: They now  have almost no speciality pizza on the menu! How can you remove traditional items like fresh mozzarella and basil?! Delivery: Small area of direct delivery. If your ordering online, like via DoorDash, there’s no pizza options. Note to Owner: Your restaurant is a part of my lifestyle! I would like to keep it that way. Please bring back your basil. And please update DoorDash (never get rid of them) with options to order pizza.
